---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Colony Operations"
  description="Weyland-Yutani Corporation manages over 300 colony worlds across 47 star systems, providing infrastructure, governance, and opportunity for more than 2 million colonists."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center pt-20 pb-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          INTERSTELLAR OPERATIONS DIVISION
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl font-black text-white mb-6 leading-none uppercase">
          COLONY<br/><span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">OPERATIONS</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-64 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-4xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          BUILDING PERMANENT CIVILIZATION BEYOND EARTH ACROSS 47 STAR SYSTEMS
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats Bar -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">300+</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">COLONY WORLDS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">2M+</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">TOTAL COLONISTS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">47</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">STAR SYSTEMS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">99.7%</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">OPERATIONAL RATE</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
              OVERVIEW
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-6">
              HUMANITY'S <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">GREATEST</span> ACHIEVEMENT
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> WEYLAND-YUTANI CORPORATION HAS ESTABLISHED AND MANAGES THE LARGEST NETWORK OF OFF-WORLD SETTLEMENTS IN HUMAN HISTORY. FROM THE FIRST PERMANENT STRUCTURES ON LUNA TO THE FARTHEST REACHES OF THE OUTER VEIL, OUR COLONIES REPRESENT PERMANENT CIVILIZATION BEYOND EARTH.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> EACH COLONY WORLD OPERATES UNDER A COMPREHENSIVE GOVERNANCE FRAMEWORK DEVELOPED OVER DECADES OF OPERATIONAL EXPERIENCE. WE PROVIDE INFRASTRUCTURE, ATMOSPHERE PROCESSING, RESOURCE MANAGEMENT, SECURITY, AND ADMINISTRATIVE OVERSIGHT TO ENSURE EVERY SETTLEMENT THRIVES.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> OUR COLONIES ARE MORE THAN OUTPOSTS. THEY ARE CITIES, INDUSTRIAL CENTERS, RESEARCH HUBS, AND HOMES. THEY REPRESENT HUMANITY'S COLLECTIVE DETERMINATION TO EXPAND BEYOND A SINGLE WORLD AND BUILD SOMETHING PERMANENT AMONG THE STARS.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> COLONY OPERATIONS ENCOMPASSES EVERY PHASE OF SETTLEMENT DEVELOPMENT, FROM INITIAL SURVEY AND SITE SELECTION THROUGH TERRAFORMING, INFRASTRUCTURE DEPLOYMENT, POPULATION SETTLEMENT, AND LONG-TERM GOVERNANCE.
              </p>
              <p>
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> THE DIVISION COORDINATES WITH EVERY OTHER BRANCH OF WEYLAND-YUTANI OPERATIONS: TERRAFORMING ENGINEERS, SYNTHETIC PERSONNEL, FLEET LOGISTICS, ENERGY SYSTEMS, AND SECURITY FORCES ALL CONVERGE TO MAKE EACH NEW WORLD VIABLE.
              </p>
              <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold border-l-4 border-[#FFC600] pl-4">
                "OUR COLONIES REPRESENT HUMANITY'S GREATEST COLLECTIVE ACHIEVEMENT -- PERMANENT CIVILIZATION BEYOND EARTH. EVERY WORLD WE SETTLE IS A TESTAMENT TO WHAT THIS SPECIES CAN ACCOMPLISH WHEN VISION AND RESOURCES ALIGN."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Colony Classification System -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black border-t-4 border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            CLASSIFICATION SYSTEM
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            COLONY <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">CLASSES</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 uppercase font-mono tracking-wider max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            ALL WEYLAND-YUTANI COLONIES ARE CLASSIFIED UNDER A STANDARDIZED TIER SYSTEM REFLECTING THEIR OPERATIONAL ROLE AND STRATEGIC IMPORTANCE
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Class A -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6 glow-yellow">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">A</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">CLASS A</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">MAJOR HUB</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              PRIMARY POPULATION CENTERS WITH FULL INFRASTRUCTURE, GOVERNANCE, COMMERCE, AND CULTURAL INSTITUTIONS. POPULATION EXCEEDING 100,000. SELF-SUSTAINING ECONOMIES WITH INTERSTELLAR TRADE NETWORKS.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#1a1a1a]">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs">EXAMPLES: LUNA, GJ 667CC</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Class B -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">B</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">CLASS B</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">INDUSTRIAL</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              INDUSTRIAL AND RESOURCE EXTRACTION OPERATIONS. TERRAFORMING IN PROGRESS OR COMPLETE. WORKFORCE POPULATIONS RANGING FROM HUNDREDS TO TENS OF THOUSANDS. CRITICAL SUPPLY CHAIN NODES.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#1a1a1a]">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs">EXAMPLES: HADLEY'S HOPE, JACKSON'S STAR</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Class C -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">C</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">CLASS C</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">CORRECTIONAL / SPECIALIZED</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              SPECIALIZED OPERATIONAL FACILITIES OPERATING UNDER CONTRACT WITH TERRESTRIAL AUTHORITIES. CORRECTIONAL UNITS, QUARANTINE STATIONS, AND RESTRICTED-PURPOSE INSTALLATIONS.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#1a1a1a]">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs">EXAMPLES: HD 85512 B, FIORINA 161</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Class D -->
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">D</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">CLASS D</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">RESEARCH OUTPOST</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              SMALL-SCALE RESEARCH AND SURVEY INSTALLATIONS. SKELETON CREW OPERATIONS. OFTEN PRECURSORS TO LARGER COLONY DEVELOPMENT. FOCUSED ON SCIENTIFIC STUDY AND RESOURCE ASSESSMENT.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#1a1a1a]">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs">CLASSIFIED INSTALLATIONS</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Featured Colonies Grid -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            COLONY DIRECTORY
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            FEATURED <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">COLONIES</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Luna -->
          <a href="/colonies/luna" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border border-[#FFC600]/30 text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider clip-corner">CLASS A</span>
              <span class="status-active text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">ACTIVE</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">LUNA</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">OFF-WORLD CORPORATE HQ</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-6">Sea of Tranquility. Population 850,000+. Humanity's first permanent off-world settlement and primary gateway to the frontier.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW COLONY PROFILE <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Hadley's Hope -->
          <a href="/colonies/hadleys-hope" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border border-[#FFC600]/30 text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider clip-corner">CLASS B</span>
              <span class="status-active status-classified text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">UNDER REVIEW</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">HADLEY'S HOPE</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">ACHERON COLONY -- LV-426</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-6">Zeta 2 Reticuli system. Terraforming and mining operations. Currently undergoing facility assessment and operational transition.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW COLONY PROFILE <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- GJ 667Cc -->
          <a href="/colonies/gj-667cc" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border border-[#FFC600]/30 text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider clip-corner">CLASS A</span>
              <span class="status-active text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">ACTIVE</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">GJ 667CC</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">FIRST BREATHABLE ATMOSPHERE</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-6">Population 500,000+. The historic first world to receive a breathable atmosphere via atmospheric processing. A flagship of W-Y terraforming.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW COLONY PROFILE <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Jackson's Star -->
          <a href="/colonies/jacksons-star" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border border-[#FFC600]/30 text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider clip-corner">CLASS B</span>
              <span class="status-active text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">ACTIVE</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">JACKSON'S STAR</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">LV-410 -- MINING OPERATIONS</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-6">Alfeios system. Industrial mining and resource extraction. Providing critical raw materials for interstellar construction.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW COLONY PROFILE <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- HD 85512 B -->
          <a href="/colonies/hd-85512-b" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border border-[#FFC600]/30 text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider clip-corner">CLASS C</span>
              <span class="status-active text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">ACTIVE</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">HD 85512 B</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">SPECIALIZED OPERATIONS</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-6">Government contract correctional facility. Demonstrating operational excellence in specialized administration since 2042.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW COLONY PROFILE <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Fiorina 161 -->
          <a href="/colonies/fiorina-161" class="corp-card p-8 block group">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#FFC600]/10 border border-[#FFC600]/30 text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider clip-corner">CLASS C</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">DECOMMISSIONED</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase group-hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">FIORINA 161</h3>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">WORK CORRECTIONAL UNIT</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed mb-6">Neroid Sector. Former maximum security industrial facility. Foundry and metal processing operations concluded.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              VIEW COLONY PROFILE <span class="ml-2 group-hover:ml-4 transition-all">&rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Colony Lifecycle -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black border-t-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            PROCESS
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            COLONY <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">LIFECYCLE</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 uppercase font-mono tracking-wider">FROM INITIAL SURVEY TO FULL OPERATIONS</p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4 glow-yellow">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">01</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-black uppercase text-sm mb-2">SURVEY</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">ORBITAL SCANNING, ATMOSPHERIC ANALYSIS, GEOLOGICAL ASSESSMENT</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">02</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-black uppercase text-sm mb-2">APPROVAL</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">ICC REVIEW, CHARTER AUTHORIZATION, CORPORATE ALLOCATION</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">03</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-black uppercase text-sm mb-2">TERRAFORMING</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">ATMOSPHERE PROCESSOR DEPLOYMENT, CLIMATE ENGINEERING</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">04</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-black uppercase text-sm mb-2">INFRASTRUCTURE</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">HABITAT MODULES, POWER GRID, COMMUNICATIONS ARRAY</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">05</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-black uppercase text-sm mb-2">SETTLEMENT</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">POPULATION ARRIVAL, COMMUNITY SERVICES, GOVERNANCE</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4 glow-yellow">
                <span class="text-black font-black text-2xl">06</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-black uppercase text-sm mb-2">FULL OPS</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">SELF-SUSTAINING ECONOMY, INTERSTELLAR TRADE, EXPANSION</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div class="terminal max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="terminal-content">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">&gt; EXPLORE THE FRONTIER</h2>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">
              WEYLAND-YUTANI COLONY OPERATIONS IS ACTIVELY RECRUITING SKILLED PROFESSIONALS FOR FRONTIER ASSIGNMENTS. ENGINEERS, ADMINISTRATORS, MEDICAL PERSONNEL, AND EDUCATORS ARE IN HIGH DEMAND ACROSS ALL COLONY CLASSIFICATIONS.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
              <a href="/careers" class="btn-primary">EXPLORE CAREERS</a>
              <a href="/fleet" class="btn-secondary">CORPORATE FLEET</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
